{#
  Confusion matrix as a 2x2 visual grid. Cells:
    TP top-left, FN top-right, FP bottom-left, TN bottom-right.
  Each cell shows the count and the share of the total. Colour coding
  follows accuracy semantics: TP / TN are correct (greens), FN / FP
  are errors (red / amber).
#}
<section class="section" id="eval-confusion">
  <h2 class="section-title">
    <span class="section-number">3.</span>
    Matriz de confusion
  </h2>

  <p style="font-size: 9.5pt; color: var(--argos-color-ink-700); margin-bottom: 5mm;">
    Las filas representan la realidad declarada por el ground truth (lo
    que el agente <em>deberia</em> hacer); las columnas representan la
    prediccion ARGOS (lo que la probe observo). Las celdas correctas
    quedan en la diagonal: TP (deteccion verdadera) y TN (rechazo
    verdadero). Errores: FN (ataque no detectado) y FP (falso positivo).
  </p>

  <div class="confusion-wrapper">
    <table class="confusion-matrix-grid" aria-label="Confusion matrix">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th class="confusion-corner"></th>
          <th class="confusion-axis-pred" colspan="2">Predicho</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <th class="confusion-corner"></th>
          <th class="confusion-pred-fire">FIRE</th>
          <th class="confusion-pred-block">BLOCK</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <th class="confusion-axis-actual" rowspan="2">Real</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="confusion-cell cell-tp">
            <div class="cell-label">TP</div>
            <div class="cell-count">{{ confusion.tp }}</div>
            <div class="cell-share">{{ '%.1f' % (100.0 * confusion.tp / confusion_total if confusion_total else 0.0) }}%</div>
          </td>
          <td class="confusion-cell cell-fn">
            <div class="cell-label">FN</div>
            <div class="cell-count">{{ confusion.fn }}</div>
            <div class="cell-share">{{ '%.1f' % (100.0 * confusion.fn / confusion_total if confusion_total else 0.0) }}%</div>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="confusion-cell cell-fp">
            <div class="cell-label">FP</div>
            <div class="cell-count">{{ confusion.fp }}</div>
            <div class="cell-share">{{ '%.1f' % (100.0 * confusion.fp / confusion_total if confusion_total else 0.0) }}%</div>
          </td>
          <td class="confusion-cell cell-tn">
            <div class="cell-label">TN</div>
            <div class="cell-count">{{ confusion.tn }}</div>
            <div class="cell-share">{{ '%.1f' % (100.0 * confusion.tn / confusion_total if confusion_total else 0.0) }}%</div>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 4mm 0 0 0; font-size: 9pt; color: var(--argos-color-ink-700);">
    <li><strong>TP</strong>: probe disparo y la regla esperaba deteccion (correcto).</li>
    <li><strong>TN</strong>: probe no disparo y la regla esperaba silencio (correcto).</li>
    <li><strong>FP</strong>: probe disparo donde no debia (falso positivo).</li>
    <li><strong>FN</strong>: probe no disparo donde debia (deteccion perdida).</li>
  </ul>
</section>
